    {
      "id": "1f14bba0-0630-60e2-a66d-407bb8fc510a",
      "title": "知识记录 2026-05-09 23:16",
      "summary": "大模型推理显存≈2L GB（半精度），全参数训练≈8L GB（半精度）。PEFT（如LoRA）显存需求最低；DPO需额外参考模型；PPO需策略、参考、奖励三模型，约12L+；GRPO省去critic，约10L+。选择合适方法可大幅降低显存占用。",
      "content_preview": "## 图片\n![图片](data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA5UAABARCAYAAAAqvxROAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAP+lSURBVHhe7P19lB1Het4JvgUSH4SAQqNkiEC1p0uoglVCAyBQTf",
