    {
      "id": "1f15db54-0321-608d-855b-0434213d1192",
      "title": "知识记录 2026-06-01 20:27",
      "summary": "OpenClaw的记忆系统是其核心能力，通过四层架构实现上下文连续性：从不可变的SOUL身份内核，到动态的TOOLS工具，再到存储用户长期记忆的USER层，最后是实时会话的Session层。系统还通过每日日志记录交互，为对话提供连续性。",
      "content_preview": "## 图片\n![图片](data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAusAAAMrCAIAAAB/BEtqAAAQAElEQVR4AeydB3xVVdbFkdBbaIFA6CAovSsgCoiAojiKqCAWBhUGUUdRBh0ddXCUD9vYEFEGUQawIIqACAgiSAelF+m9917C9082nLm+9xKSl4T3kqz8to",
