    {
      "id": "1f15db56-26fb-651c-a5f8-5320a4489689",
      "title": "知识记录 2026-06-01 20:28",
      "summary": "Agent配置支持白名单机制，允许特定平台用户（如Telegram、WhatsApp、Discord）直接对话，跳过配对。群聊中默认只响应@提及的消息，可切换为始终响应模式以提高互动，但token消耗较高。通过命令`/activation mention|always`可动态调整行为。",
      "content_preview": "## 图片\n![图片](data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAtEAAAJQCAIAAADHR68tAAAQAElEQVR4AeydCbxO1frH7zEdnMwdl8ykTMk8JmS8ElHchItrKqI0KqU0SCFFFHLREWXKnHnIlDHzkDFDhMzHdND/e86T3f6/57yvMznj7/08rZ79rGevvd",
