      "title": "知识记录 2026-06-01 20:28",
      "summary": "OpenClaw是一个以Unix哲学为核心的极简AI Agent框架，主张用最少工具做最多事。它强调命令行接口作为通用交互方式，仅提供读、写、编辑和执行四个基础工具，追求高效、轻量、可组合的系统设计。",
      "content_preview": "## 图片\n![图片](data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAtgAAAJPCAIAAADJ0jSpAAAQAElEQVR4AezdCbzXc/Y/8DaiFEURNUURWbJlzdhDdrIzlmxj/dlmGMww1hm7wVgHw5B9iVSIrBGFhFKUIkIpSiX8n7c3n//H93vv7da91a177uPM2/mc93",
